profile:
Executive carpentry and renovations provides Kitchener, Waterloo, and Cambridge with more residentials and light commercial carpentry services than any other company. We do this by understanding your wants and needs, we provide interior finish services, exterior finish services, rough carpentry framing, and general contracting services.
Our customers are extremely satisfied with our workmanship, customer service, timeline management, and professionalism, oh not forgetting we are insured.
Contact us today for a smooth project and we will bring your dream to life, big or small.
